        "TileImage": "$($repository 87be73e8-64a2-4381-8438-013bb5d4f241).Image",
        "Description": "47, we have an update on your mission.\rAs you  know,  you need to eliminate Noel Crest, the old former operative of Lucas Grey. Our target is now in business with Akka, the leader of the pirates. The ICA wants us to kill the pirate queen. We can use this opportunity to kill both of the targets.\rBut now, we&apos;ve learn that Orson Mills, the leader of the Crest security and Farah, the owner of the local bar are also involved in the vendetta against Providence. We need to kill them all. Good luck 47.",
